  "body": "### Description\n\nI'm developing a command line Quarkus application that I want to execute as a Kubernetes Job. \r\n\r\nIf I add the Kubernetes extension, it's not creating a Kubernetes Job but a Deployment. Also, if I try to configure the `kind` through `application.properties`, it says that only Deployment or StatefulSet is possible.\r\n\r\nI think as a first step, it would be nice to be able to set the kind Job. But as a second step, it would be nice to detect the `QuarkusMain` annotation and automatically create a `Job`.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
